Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and enlightening depiction of a radiant, divine figure standing amidst a backdrop of celestial clouds and golden light. The figure exudes a sense of majesty and grace, embodying the concept of a benevolent and omnipotent deity. The scene should evoke a feeling of spiritual awe and inspiration, resonating with themes of faith and reverence in a visually captivating manner.
